			<section id='overview'>
				<div class="medium-8 medium-centered columns">
					<h1>Emotions have Layers</h1>
					<p>Emotions are complicated, and identifying or explaining them can be difficult for young children. We feel more than just "sad" or "happy." What about betrayed or grateful or jealous? Emoshkas are nesting dolls meant to help young children with emotional learning and conflict resolution.</p>
				</div>

				<div class='video-wrapper'>
