			<section id='highfi'>
				<div class="medium-8 medium-centered columns">
					<h1>Prototyping Finesse</h1>
					<p>We upgraded each component of our Emoshkas iteratively. First, we moved from a cardboard base to lasercutting acrylic and plywood. Then we used store-bought wooden dolls to glue magnets and embed wires, before finally testing it all together with Arduino code and neopixel components. </p>
